Author: ICOproducer
Title: [ANN][ICO] SINTEC - A UNIQUE BLOCKCHAIN OPTION FOR A PRODUCT IN A REAL INDUSTRY.
Body: SINTEC - A UNIQUE BLOCKCHAIN OPTION FOR A PRODUCT IN A REAL INDUSTRY   IMPORTANT INFORMATION! All the relevant information about this project is on the page 2!  Moderator - AdmSintec  WEBSITE / WHITE PAPER / TWITTER /FACEBOOK / TELEGRAM / MEDIUM  Our official bounty thread  Sintec - is a unique Blockchain option granting the opportunity to invest in the production of high-tech industrial material - polymer bituminous binders (PBB).  What are polymer bituminous binders?  Polymer bituminous binders are polymeric composites made from high molecular petroleum solvents, polymers and fillers, contained in the polymers of protonated complexes of various modifiers. The main difference in the applied technologies for the modification of bituminous rubber crumbs lays in the nano molecular transformation of raw material.  Where is it used?  Road building Accumulator mastic manufacturing Waterproofing Cable production Paints and varnishes Roof building material  Mechanism for gaining earnings on STEC tokens 1.Investors acquire STEC tokens during the ICO, which are backed by a real product - PBB and are considered to be a Blockchain-option, sold at a 50%. 2.Starting from March 2019. Sintec will open a company for the repurchase of $1.6 million dollars worth of tokens on a monthly basis. 3.Tokens which are not claimed for redemption during March 2019, will earn 8.5% dividends per annum, credited each month.  Sintec - this is the only project that compensates lost profits in the case that the rate of invested cryptocurrencies rises!  Guarantees  By buying STEC tokens during the ICO, investors receive a guarantee that their initial investment will grow by over 100%. In order for this to happen, investors simply need to declare their intent to sell tokens at any time, starting March 2019. STEC tokens are backed by raw materials - polymer bituminous binders. Starting March 2019, any investors will be able to exchange his tokens for raw materials at the first demand. During the time of the ICO, the cost of 1 ton of raw materials will be fixed to 21 000 rub. If a request for a repurchase is submitted, and the cost of the raw material grows, then the cost of the token will grow proportionately. If the cost of the cryptocurrency that the investor used as an investment grows when STEC tokens are presented for a buyback, tokens will be able to be returned at the going rate. Thus, investing in STEC also means that you are investing in Bitcoins, Ethereum, and Waves. If an investor decides to sell tokens immediately after March 2019. Then that investor will will earn 8.5% dividends per annum, credited each month.  STEC TOKEN  Token Name: STEC Platform: Ethereum Token Standard: ERC 20 Hard Cap: 30 000 000 USD Soft Cap 16 000 000 USD Cost of a STEC Token: 1 STEC = 5 USD Backing: 14 kg PBB  Early investors get the following bonus when purchasing STEC tokens during the I Stage of ICO:  1-3 days - 50% discount 4-6 days - 40% discount 7-13 days - 35% discount 14-20 days - 30% discount 21-26 days - 25% discount 27-30 days - 20% discount

Author: ICOproducer
Title: [ANN][ICO] SINTEC - A UNIQUE BLOCKCHAIN OPTION FOR A PRODUCT IN A REAL INDUSTRY.
Body: Thank you for your questions and issues.  To ensure the transparency of the financial and technological flows of the project, the blockchain electronic document management system (BEDMS) will be used on the basis of an electronic document circulation system with open source Alfresco Community Editions and database on the blockchain. All ongoing financial payments and deductions, contracts, internal project documents, internal documents of the project production invoices for production leave, will be signed electronically and registered in the blockchain (similar to BEDMS DocSensus of Deloitte).Thus, any investor will be able to fully control all stages of project implementation, shipment of finished products, etc.  Moreover, Sintec team have already a future agreement for the sale of 12 500 tons of our raw material per month!  For more detailed information you can get acquainted with Whitepaper http://www.sintec.io/static/ver107/pages/whitepaper/en.pdf  If you still have any questions feel free to ask. Author: ICOproducer
Title: [ANN][ICO] SINTEC - A UNIQUE BLOCKCHAIN OPTION FOR A PRODUCT IN A REAL INDUSTRY.
Body: Thank you for your question, let me explain you. You will double your investments if you buy SINT tokens during the first three days of ICO, as you will have a 50% discount on them. And then, starting from March 2019 Sintec will open a company for the repurchase of $1.6 million dollars worth of tokens on a monthly basis. That's why you will grow your investments by over 100%. Example: Let's say the purchase amount is 1000 USD. On the first day of the investment campaign with a 50% discount and the cost of 1 SINT = 2.50 USD you can buy: 1000 USD : 2,50 USD = 400 SINT. The redemption on March 1, 2019: 400 SINT x 5 USD = 2000 USD. Thus, the invested funds are doubled.
